<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 21:14:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国无人机制造商更换五角大楼案件律师，放弃洛雷塔·林奇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/chinese-drone-maker-changes-lawyers-pentagon-case-dropping-loretta-lynch-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国无人机制造商大疆创新在针对美国国防部的诉讼中更换了其法律团队，将奥巴马时代的美国司法部长洛雷塔·林奇及其法律团队替换为奎因·伊曼纽尔·厄克特沙利文律师事务所的新律师。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 20:07:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/chinese-drone-maker-changes-lawyers-pentagon-case-dropping-loretta-lynch-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国对中国芯片产业实施新限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-chip-industry-with-new-restrictions-2024-12-02/</link><description>美国周一对中国半导体行业发起了三年来的第三次严厉打击，限制了对包括芯片设备制造商北方华创科技集团在内的 140 家公司的出口。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 19:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-chip-industry-with-new-restrictions-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>报告称中国激光雷达传感器对美国国防设备构成黑客风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-lidar-sensors-pose-hacking-risk-us-defense-equipment-report-says-2024-12-02/</link><description>华盛顿智库周一发布的报告称，中国制造的激光雷达传感器可能会使美国军方在冲突期间遭受黑客攻击和破坏，该报告呼吁禁止将这些传感器安装到美国国防设备中。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-lidar-sensors-pose-hacking-risk-us-defense-equipment-report-says-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国新一轮打击中国芯片出口后，ASML 并未改变指导方针</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-does-not-expect-us-export-curbs-hit-long-term-chip-sector-demand-2024-12-02/</link><description>计算机芯片设备制造商ASML表示，预计美国周一宣布的对中国半导体出口的新限制不会影响其最新的财务指引。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-does-not-expect-us-export-curbs-hit-long-term-chip-sector-demand-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国对东南亚征收新的太阳能关税将提高价格、削减利润率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/new-us-solar-tariffs-southeast-asia-raise-prices-cut-profit-margins-2024-12-02/</link><description>分析师表示，美国对东南亚生产商征收的新一轮太阳能电池板进口关税预计将提高消费者价格并削减生产商利润率，但这在很大程度上是业界预期的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 10:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/new-us-solar-tariffs-southeast-asia-raise-prices-cut-profit-margins-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫称特朗普就美元问题向金砖国家发出威胁将适得其反</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-trump-threat-brics-nations-against-replacing-us-dollar-will-2024-12-02/</link><description>克里姆林宫周一表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁称，如果金砖国家创造自己的货币，将对它们征收关税，美国任何强迫各国使用美元的企图都会适得其反。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-trump-threat-brics-nations-against-replacing-us-dollar-will-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国移动提出以 8.82 亿美元收购香港宽带网络</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-hkbn-gets-rival-takeover-interest-i-squared-capital-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国移动周一表示，已提出收购香港宽频 (HKBN)，该交易对这家香港宽带公司的估值为 68.6 亿港元（合 8.82 亿美元），旨在对抗一家私募股权公司的举动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:40:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-hkbn-gets-rival-takeover-interest-i-squared-capital-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔能源公司与壳牌签署向中国交付液化天然气的长期协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/qatarenergy-signs-long-term-lng-deal-with-shell-delivery-china-2024-12-02/</link><description>国有卡塔尔能源公司 (QATPE.UL) 与石油和天然气巨头壳牌公司签署了一项长期销售和采购协议，为其提供液化天然气 (LNG) 并运往中国，</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/qatarenergy-signs-long-term-lng-deal-with-shell-delivery-china-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>部长表示，印尼尚未与北京就南海联合开发区达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-yet-agree-joint-development-areas-with-beijing-south-china-sea-2024-12-02/</link><description>印度尼西亚外交部长周一表示，尚未决定与中国在南海的任何联合开发区域，以减轻人们对最近与北京达成的协议可能损害其主权的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-yet-agree-joint-development-areas-with-beijing-south-china-sea-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>为了寻求更高的利润，Stellantis首席执行官塔瓦雷斯失去了一些核心客户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/seeking-higher-margins-stellantis-ceo-tavares-lost-some-core-customers-2024-12-02/</link><description>Stellantis 大众市场品牌不断上涨的价格驱走了受通货膨胀影响的顾客。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:52:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/seeking-higher-margins-stellantis-ceo-tavares-lost-some-core-customers-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国债券持续上涨，10年期国债收益率跌破2%，创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-relentless-bond-rally-pushes-10-year-yield-below-2-lowest-record-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国10年期国债收益率周一跌破2%，触及历史最低点，打破了心理障碍，因为经济不景气和进一步降息的押注促使投资者转向安全的债券。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-relentless-bond-rally-pushes-10-year-yield-below-2-lowest-record-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中方谴责立陶宛驱逐其外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-opposes-lithuania-declaring-its-diplomats-persona-non-grata-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，强烈谴责并坚决反对立陶宛将三名中国驻​​立临时代办外交官列为不受欢迎的人。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:57:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-opposes-lithuania-declaring-its-diplomats-persona-non-grata-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>澳门未来领导人公布管理赌博中心的团队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/macaus-future-leader-unveils-team-govern-gambling-hub-2024-12-02/</link><description>澳门候任行政长官公布了从12月20日起管理这个全球最大赌场中心的官员团队，其中包括一位经验丰富的经济部长，其职责是实现经济多元化并减少对赌博收入的依赖。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:08:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/macaus-future-leader-unveils-team-govern-gambling-hub-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>总统在夏威夷表示台湾是高科技领域值得信赖的合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-speaks-about-china-with-ex-speaker-pelosi-while-hawaii-2024-12-02/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德对夏威夷智囊团表示，台湾与美国的伙伴关系是包括半导体行业在内的高科技产业的力量源泉，并表明台湾是值得信赖和可靠的合作伙伴。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:06:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-speaks-about-china-with-ex-speaker-pelosi-while-hawaii-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国对中国芯片的最新打压打击了半导体工具制造商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/latest-us-strike-chinas-chips-hits-semiconductor-toolmakers-2024-12-02/</link><description>美国将于周一对中国半导体行业发起三年来的第三次打压，限制对140家企业的出口。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 05:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/latest-us-strike-chinas-chips-hits-semiconductor-toolmakers-2024-12-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>